pd_0_com_0text: This island’s booty has been rumoured all o'er Tortuga in drunken ramblings from those in power.
pd_0_com_1text: The word o' loot spreads wit' haste. Hopefully we be the first here.
pd_1_com_0text: They spoke o' a civilisation based around the idea o' peace fer all. 'tis wha' be left o' it. Naught but a faint memory o' serenity.
pd_2_com_0text: Enough wit' the chit-chat, let's get goin'.
pd_3_com_0text: Seems we be nah alone here. We ought t' hurry up.
pd_4_com_0text: Stop! 'tis where the booty be. It's time t' dig lads.
pd_5_com_0text: Lucky fer us thar treasury was nah found by the army. That goddamn black spotted -
pd_6_com_0text: This black spotted monarchy. The royal army needs t' be stopped.
pd_7_com_1text: The island was found, raided 'n every scallywag that lived here either died on thar knees or was taken captive.
pd_8_com_0text: This island used t' be home t' a civilisation o' peaceful farmers that minded thar owns business 'n stayed far away from any politics.
pd_9_com_0text: Arrr! Let's bring it t' the Cap'n!
